#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector\\_norm"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:1 of
msgid "Computes the vector norm of a vector (or batch of vectors) ``x``."
msgstr "计算向量（或向量批次）``x`` 的向量范数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:3 of
msgid "This function is Array API compatible."
msgstr "此函数与 Array API 兼容。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:5 of
msgid "Input array."
msgstr "输入数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:7 of
msgid ""
"If an integer, ``axis`` specifies the axis (dimension) along which to "
"compute vector norms. If an n-tuple, ``axis`` specifies the axes "
"(dimensions) along which to compute batched vector norms. If ``None``, "
"the vector norm must be computed over all array values (i.e., equivalent "
"to computing the vector norm of a flattened array). Default: ``None``."
msgstr ""
"如果为整数，``axis`` 指定计算向量范数的轴（维度）。如果为 n 元组，``axis`"
"` 指定计算批处理向量范数的轴（维度）。如果为 ``None``，则必须计算所有数组"
"值的向量范数（即等效于计算展平数组的向量范数）。默认值：``None``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:14 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are normed over are left in the "
"result as dimensions with size one. Default: False."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则在结果中保留用于计算范数的轴，其大小为 1。默认值："
"False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:17 of
msgid ""
"The order of the norm. For details see the table under ``Notes`` in "
"`numpy.linalg.norm`."
msgstr "范数的阶数。详情请参见 `numpy.linalg.norm` 中 ``Notes`` 下的表格。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.linalg.norm`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:24 of
msgid "Generic norm function"
msgstr "通用范数函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vector_norm.vector_norm:27 of
